@title PistolPoniesGameSave
 @dev Extensible on-chain game save storage with micro-fee
 
 Supports flexible data storage with versioning for future updates:
 - Core stats (name, kills, deaths, level)
 - Skill stats (speed, health, ammo, jump, dash, aim)
 - Inventory (weapons, items as encoded data)
 - Achievements (badge IDs)
 - Settings (player preferences as encoded data)
 - Match history (wins, losses, playtime)
 - Cosmetics (skins, colors, accessories)
 
 Uses key-value storage for extensibility - new data types can be added
 without contract redeployment.
@dev Save all game data at once (most common use case)
@dev Batch save multiple data entries (costs 1 fee total)
